<plot>A beautiful woman moves demurely, but with a hint of seduction. It's impossible to tell that the beautiful woman we're seeing up on the stage is actually played by a man. THE WORLDS OF MEI LANFANG reveals the life and career of Mei Lanfang -- who became an international sensation for his portrayals of women.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?602373</url></doc>
